<body>
    <h1>PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
    <p>Last updated: January 27, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Elevyn (“we,” “us,” or “our”) values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and
        protect your information when you use our Services.</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3>a. Personal Information</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Account credentials</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>b. Health & Fitness Data</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Body measurements (estimated via scans)</li>
        <li>Fitness goals</li>
        <li>Workout and nutrition data</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>c. Images & Media</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Photos uploaded for body scans or food scans</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>d. Technical Data</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Device type</li>
        <li>IP address</li>
        <li>App usage data</li>
        <li>Analytics and crash data</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your data to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and improve the Services</li>
        <li>Power AI features (body scan, food scan, recommendations)</li>
        <li>Manage subscriptions and payments</li>
        <li>Communicate updates and support</li>
        <li>Ensure security and prevent misuse</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. AI & Data Processing</h2>
    <p>Uploaded images and data may be processed by AI systems to generate insights.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Images are not sold</li>
        <li>Data is used only to deliver App functionality</li>
        <li>We do not use your data to identify you outside the App</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share limited data with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Payment processors (e.g., Apple, Google, Stripe)</li>
        <li>Analytics providers</li>
        <li>Cloud infrastructure providers</li>
    </ul>
    <p>All partners are required to maintain data protection standards.</p>

    <h2>6. Data Storage & Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot
        guarantee absolute security.</p>

    <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location, you may have the right to: Access your data, Correct your data, Delete your account
        and personal data, Withdraw consent.</p>
    <p>Requests can be made by contacting us.</p>

    <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your data only as long as necessary to provide the Services or comply with legal obligations.</p>

    <h2>9. Children’s Privacy</h2>
    <p>Elevyn is not intended for individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect data from minors.</p>

    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be effective upon posting.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions or requests:</p>
    <p>By email: <a href="mailto:support@elevyn.com">support@elevyn.com</a></p>
